sion outside of the jet cone. The found effect seems\nrather small. More refine calculation requires full simulation of $c$- and\n$b$-jets which goes beyond of the scope of the present paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2022 17:16:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2022 14:28:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-05"}
