ss of Q1D multiband superconducting\nmaterials, encouraging further experiments aimed at reaching larger critical\ntemperatures in such multiband superconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2022 18:39:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2022 20:08:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-01"}
